ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRefugee Protection Division Rules
PrecisREFUGEE PROTECTION DIVISION RULES in order to make an important contribution to the overall objectives of the Balanced Refugee Reform Act and the Protecting Canada's Immigration System Act which are to ensure the faster processing of claims, faster removals for failed claimants, and the deterrence of non-genuine claims.
